41:52.480 --> 41:55.643
Richard, who was with me
got uncharacteristically quiet

41:55.800 --> 41:59.282
And he said, "All things considered,
I guess you don't have to buy it"

41:59.440 --> 42:05.447
So I smile like Mona Lisa
and I lay my Visa down

42:06.600 --> 42:09.968
He wants me
He wants me

42:10.120 --> 42:13.010
