42:13.160 --> 42:14.161
Damn right!

42:14.320 --> 42:16.891
I've found my guiding light

42:17.040 --> 42:20.249
I tell the stars each night

42:20.400 --> 42:23.961
Look at me
Look at him

42:24.360 --> 42:30.402
Son of a bitch,
I guess I'm doing something right

42:31.160 --> 42:37.202
