46:44.800 --> 46:47.929
Please don't expect that from me

46:48.080 --> 46:51.687
I will be late
But if you can just wait

46:51.840 --> 46:55.447
I will make it eventually

46:55.600 --> 46:58.843
Not like it's in my control

46:59.040 --> 47:02.442
Not like I'm proud of the fact

47:02.600 --> 47:07.288
