I don't know why people run

47:15.160 --> 47:18.801
I don't know why things fall through

47:18.960 --> 47:22.965
I don't know how anybody
survives in this life

47:23.120 --> 47:26.090
Without someone like you

47:26.280 --> 47:29.762
I could protect and preserve

47:29.920 --> 47:33.970
I could say no and goodbye

47:34.160 --> 47:38.210
But why, Jamie?

47:38.360 --> 47:41.364
Why?

47:41.520 --> 47:47.482
I want to be your wife

47:48.840 --> 47:54.847
I want to bear your child

47:56.600 --> 48:01.640
I want to die, knowing I

48:01.800 --> 48:04.724
Had a long, full life

48:04.880 --> 48:10.887
In your arms

