Cathy? Where are you going?

01:08:36.640 --> 01:08:39.448
Cathy? Cathy?!

01:08:40.171 --> 01:08:42.126
Cathy! Stop!

01:08:58.600 --> 01:08:59.805
Uh, you know they're gonna love me.

