You don't have to get a haircut

01:11:27.800 --> 01:11:30.724
You don't have to change your shoes

01:11:30.880 --> 01:11:34.089
You don't have to like Duran Duran

01:11:34.240 --> 01:11:35.321
Just one song!

01:11:35.520 --> 01:11:37.090
Just love me

01:11:37.240 --> 01:11:40.403
You don't have to put the seat down

01:11:40.560 --> 01:11:43.769
You don't have to watch the news

01:11:43.920 --> 01:11:46.685
You don't have to learn to tango

01:11:46.840 --> 01:11:50.208
You don't have to eat prosciutto

01:11:50.360 --> 01:11:52.647
You don't have to change a thing

01:11:52.800 --> 01:11:58.728
Just stay with me

01:11:58.880 --> 01:12:02.805
I want you and you and nothing but you

01:12:03.000 --> 01:12:05.241
Miles and piles of you

01:12:05.400 --> 01:12:08.370
Finally, I'll have something worthwhile

01:12:08.520 --> 01:12:11.683
To think of each morning

01:12:11.840 --> 01:12:15.208
You and you and nothing but you

01:12:15.360 --> 01:12:17.727
No substitution will do

01:12:17.880 --> 01:12:20.963
Nothing but fresh undiluted and pure

01:12:21.120 --> 01:12:26.365
Top of the line

01:12:26.520 --> 01:12:32.527
And totally mine

01:12:34.240 --> 01:12:36.686
I don't need any lifetime commitments

01:12:36.840 --> 01:12:39.730
I don't need to get hitched tonight

01:12:40.440 --> 01:12:45.731
I don't want you to throw up
all your walls and defenses

01:12:46.720 --> 01:12:49.087
I don't mean to put on any pressure

01:12:49.240 --> 01:12:52.244
But I know when a thing is right

01:12:53.000 --> 01:12:57.562
And I spend every day
reconfiguring my senses

01:12:58.160 --> 01:13:01.642
When we get to my house
take a look at that town

01:13:01.800 --> 01:13:04.167
Take a look at how far I've gone

01:13:04.320 --> 01:13:10.362
I will never go back
Never look back anymore

01:13:10.720 --> 01:13:14.167
And it feels like my life
led right to your side

01:13:14.320 --> 01:13:17.324
And will keep me there from now on

01:13:17.480 --> 01:13:20.848
Think about what you wanted

01:13:21.040 --> 01:13:23.771
Think about what could be

01:13:23.960 --> 01:13:26.964
Think about how I love you

01:13:27.120 --> 01:13:30.090
And say you'll move in with me

01:13:30.240 --> 01:13:33.164
Think of what's great about me and you

01:13:33.320 --> 01:13:36.085
Think of the bullshit
we've both been through

01:13:36.240 --> 01:13:42.247
Think of what's past
because we can do better

01:13:44.000 --> 01:13:49.530
We can do better

